OL,4,CBacklash against longer hours to ease
OL,5,Clorry driver shortage
OL,6, A temporary extension of lorry drivers'
OL,7, working hours has been met with
OL,8, backlash from the industry who say the
OL,9, government is applying a "sticking
OL,10, plaster" to driver shortage problems.
OL,12,FHGV drivers can increase their daily
OL,13,Fdriving limits from nine to 10 hours or
OL,14,Fchange weekly rest patterns on Monday.
OL,16,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said
OL,17,Fthe move would give flexibility to
OL,18,Fdrivers to make slightly longer trips.
OL,20,FBut the Road Haulage Association said
OL,21,Fthe move wouldn't make any difference.
